#: content/community/calendar/2026/akademy.md:24
msgid ""
"Akademy is the annual world summit of KDE, one of the largest Free Software "
"communities in the world. It is a free, non-commercial event organized by "
"the KDE Community. This year we will celebrate the 30th years of KDE in "
"Graz."
msgstr ""

