msgid "https://community.kde.org/Sprints/MegaSprint/2026"
msgstr ""

#: content/community/calendar/2026/megasprint.md:18
msgid ""
"The sprint will be held the week before Grazer Linuxtage and extending "
"through the weekend. Contributors working on KDE Goals, as well as on "
"Plasma, Frameworks, Apps, and everything in between, are invited to join. If"
" you’re interested in attending, please join the [Sprint Graz 2026 matrix "
"room](https://matrix.to/#/#sprint-graz-2026:kde.org) so we can start "
"coordinating and discussing topics you’d like to work on."
msgstr ""

